{"lemma":"سَحُورُ","slug":"سَحُورُ","root":"س.ح.ر","root_slug":"س-ح-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ح-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19083","n19084"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"suhur"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of سَحَرَ (saḥara) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sa.ħuːr/","/su.ħuːr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19083","headword_ar":"سَحُورٌ","root":"sHr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A meal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"food,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, TA,) or [particularly]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sawiyq","text_ar":"سَوِيق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[generally meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meal of parched barley"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is eaten at the time called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHar","text_ar":"سَحَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, * Mgh, Msb, K* TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a draught of milk that is drunk at that time."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) It is repeatedly mentioned in trads. [relating to Ramadán, when the Muslim is required to be exact in the time of this meal], and mostly as above; but some say that it is correctly [in these cases] with damm, [i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suHuwr","text_ar":"سُحُور"},{"kind":"text","text":", which see below,] because the blessing and recompense have respect to the action, and not to the food. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n19084","headword_ar":"سُحُورٌ","root":"sHr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", an inf. n. [without a verb properly belonging to it, or rather a quasi-inf. n., for its verb is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasaH~ara","text_ar":"تَسَحَّرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (TA,) The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eating the meal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"food,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drinking the draught of milk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHuwr","text_ar":"سَحُور"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (Msb, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]}]}}